<br>
&lt;Original Epic&gt;<br>
Kill Naggy<br>
Wait 72 Hours for Merchant version of Ragefire<br>
Turn in Pearl.<br>
Kill Human Ragefire<br>
Kill Dragon Rage<br>
Loot Heart.<br>
Turn in Heart in TD. <br>
Turn in Orbs<br>
Congrats on Epic. <br>
<br>
&lt;Original Skyfire Version of Rage&gt;<br>
Find Merchant version of Rage in SOL B<br>
Turn in Pearl, get another pearl back.<br>
Sit on ass for an ungodly amount of time in skyfire.<br>
Kill Human Rage<br>
Kill Dragon Rage<br>
Loot Heart<br>
Combine Heart and Pearl<br>
Turn in Heart in TD<br>
Turn In Orbs<br>
Congrats on Epic<br>
<br>
&lt;Skyfire Version as it stands now , may not be 100% accurate&gt;<br>
<br>
Turn in Pearl in Solb to Merchant Rage , Get another Pearl.<br>
Speak to NPC in skyfire (unsure of name) , Get Shard Container.<br>
Kill Wurms and Chromatic's till you have 4 shards. <br>
Place shards in Container , Click Combine<br>
Turn in Combined Container to NPC that gave you the bag<br>
Kill Human Rage<br>
Kill Dragon Rage<br>
Loot Heart<br>
Combine Heart and Pearl (Not sure if this is still the case here)<br>
Turn in Heart in TD<br>
Turn in Orbs<br>
Congrats on Epic<br>
